==English==
===Pronunciation===
*IPA: /meˈtælədʒi/
===Etymology===
Greek "metal" + "work"
===Noun===
'''metallurgy'''
# The [[science]] of [[metal]]s; their [[extraction]] from [[ore]]s, [[purification]] and [[alloy]]ing, [[heat]] [[treatment]], and [[working]].

